title: #92Noon! 10am Hour 11/2 Matt Daniels, Doug Williams
description: --Vikings STC Matt Daniels joins the show from TCO to discuss House of the Dragon, Game of Thrones, and some Vikings special teams. Then Super Bowl winner Doug Williams joins for the first time!
